high_descs: Walk to the sink to your left.
Pick up the egg sitting on the ledge of the counter between the lettuce and apple.
Place the egg inside the microwave, cook it then remove it.
With the egg, look down and walk to the waste basket to your left.
Place the cooked egg inside the waste basket.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked egg inside the waste basket.

high_descs: Go forward, turn to the sink on the left.
Pick up the egg that is on the sink.
Raise the egg up to the microwave.
Put the egg into the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the egg when it is done cooking.
Hang a left, go to the garbage can at the end of the counter.
Put the egg in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked egg in a garbage can.

high_descs: walk forward then turn left towards the sink
pick up egg from the sink
place egg in microwave cook the egg  and pull it back out
turn left walk forward and turn right at the trash can
throw egg in the trash can
anns.task_desc: cook the egg from the sink and then throw it in the trash can
